<i>noun</i>: 약주 [약쭈], 술 [술] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>약주 [약쭈]</dt><br>
<dd>1. medicinal wine</dd><br>
<dd>약으로 마시는 술.</dd><br>
<dd>A liquor that one drinks as a medicine.</dd><br>
<dd>2. liquor; wine; spirits</dd><br>
<dd>(점잖게 이르는 말로) 술.</dd><br>
<dd>(refined) An alcoholic drink.</dd><br>
<dd>3. pure liquor</dd><br>
<dd>다 익은 술에 맑은 부분만 떠낸 술.</dd><br>
<dd>A clear liquor made by straining a fermented liquor.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>술 [술]</dt><br>
<dd>alcohol; liquor</dd><br>
<dd>맥주나 소주 등과 같이 알코올 성분이 들어 있어서 마시면 취하는 음료.</dd><br>
<dd>A beverage that contains alcoholic ingredients so that one gets drunk if one drinks it, such as beer, soju, Korean distilled liquor, etc.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>